#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:89
msgid ""
"The attention backends that implement `update_graph_params()` are "
"`PagedAttention` and `BlockManagerAttention`."
msgstr "实现 `update_graph_params()` 的注意力后端是 `PagedAttention` 和 `BlockManagerAttention`。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:91
msgid ""
"The current implementation uses a synchronous update pattern: the host "
"waits for the update stream to finish before replay begins. This is "
"simpler to reason about and sufficient for current workloads. An "
"asynchronous pattern that overlaps update with replay is possible in "
"principle but not yet implemented."
msgstr "当前实现使用同步更新模式：主机等待更新流完成后再开始重放。这样更容易推理，并且对于当前工作负载来说已经足够。异步模式在原则上可以重叠更新和重放，但尚未实现。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:93
msgid "Piecewise graph capture and replay"
msgstr "分段图捕获与重放"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:95
msgid ""
"Piecewise mode captures each model layer as a separate ACL graph. This "
"reduces per-graph memory pressure and makes it feasible to capture larger"
" batch sizes on Ascend. The trade-off is that each layer incurs a replay "
"launch, so the host overhead saved by graph mode is partially offset by "
"the number of segments."
msgstr "分段模式将每个模型层捕获为单独的 ACL 计算图。这减少了每个计算图的内存压力，使得在 Ascend 上捕获更大的批次大小成为可能。代价是每层都会产生一次重放启动，因此计算图模式节省的主机开销会被分段数量部分抵消。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:97
msgid ""
"Piecewise capture is implemented in "
"`vllm_ascend.compilation.acl_graph.ACLGraphWrapper._capture_piecewise()`."
" The wrapper iterates over the model layers, captures each one "
"individually, and stores the resulting graph handles in a list. During "
"replay, `_replay_piecewise()` replays each segment in order."
msgstr "分段捕获在 `vllm_ascend.compilation.acl_graph.ACLGraphWrapper._capture_piecewise()` 中实现。封装器遍历模型层，单独捕获每一层，并将生成的计算图句柄存储在列表中。在重放期间，`_replay_piecewise()` 按顺序重放每个段。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:99
msgid ""
"Piecewise mode does not require the host-side attention parameter update "
"mechanism described above, because each layer's graph is small enough "
"that the attention parameters are captured as part of the graph itself."
msgstr "分段模式不需要上述的主机端注意力参数更新机制，因为每层的计算图足够小，注意力参数可以作为计算图本身的一部分被捕获。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:101
msgid "Graph pool management"
msgstr "计算图池管理"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:103
msgid ""
"ACL graph capture requires a memory pool that persists across captures. "
"The pool is created once during the first capture and reused for "
"subsequent captures of the same batch descriptor. The pool is destroyed "
"when the `ACLGraphWrapper` is garbage collected or when the model is "
"reloaded."
msgstr "ACL 计算图捕获需要一个跨捕获持久化的内存池。该池在第一次捕获期间创建一次，并用于同一批次描述符的后续捕获。当 `ACLGraphWrapper` 被垃圾回收或模型重新加载时，该池被销毁。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:105
msgid ""
"The pool is managed by `torch.npu.graph_pool_handle()` and "
"`torch.npu.graph_pool_handle_destroy()`. The current implementation "
"creates one pool per batch descriptor, which is sufficient for the "
"typical number of capture sizes. If the number of capture sizes grows "
"significantly, pool memory may become a concern."
msgstr "该池由 `torch.npu.graph_pool_handle()` 和 `torch.npu.graph_pool_handle_destroy()` 管理。当前实现为每个批次描述符创建一个池，这对于典型的捕获大小数量来说已经足够。如果捕获大小数量显著增长，池内存可能会成为一个问题。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:107
msgid "Error handling and fallback"
msgstr "错误处理与回退"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:109
msgid ""
"If ACL graph capture fails for any reason (e.g., out of memory, stream "
"resource exhaustion, unsupported operator), the wrapper falls back to "
"eager execution for that batch descriptor. The failure is logged but does"
" not crash the model. Subsequent requests for the same batch descriptor "
"will attempt capture again, which may succeed if the resource situation "
"has changed."
msgstr "如果 ACL 计算图捕获因任何原因失败（例如，内存不足、流资源耗尽、不支持的算子），封装器会为该批次描述符回退到立即执行模式。失败会被记录，但不会导致模型崩溃。后续对同一批次描述符的请求将再次尝试捕获，如果资源情况已发生变化，则可能成功。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:111
msgid ""
"Similarly, if replay fails (e.g., due to a device error), the wrapper "
"falls back to eager execution for that request and logs the error. The "
"graph is not evicted from the cache on replay failure, because the "
"failure may be transient."
msgstr "类似地，如果重放失败（例如，由于设备错误），封装器会为该请求回退到立即执行模式并记录错误。重放失败时不会从缓存中驱逐该计算图，因为失败可能是暂时的。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:113
msgid "Future Work"
msgstr "未来工作"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:115
msgid ""
"The current implementation is functional but has several areas for "
"improvement:"
msgstr "当前实现功能完整，但有几个改进方向："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:117
msgid ""
"Asynchronous attention parameter update: overlapping host-side update "
"with replay could reduce latency further."
msgstr "异步注意力参数更新：将主机端更新与重放重叠可以进一步减少延迟。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:118
msgid ""
"Dynamic capture size adjustment: the current stream budget trimming is "
"static. A dynamic approach that adjusts capture sizes based on actual "
"resource usage could improve coverage."
msgstr "动态捕获大小调整：当前的流预算裁剪是静态的。基于实际资源使用情况动态调整捕获大小的方法可以提高覆盖率。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:119
msgid ""
"Full graph support for encoder-decoder models: currently forced to "
"piecewise mode, but full graph may be feasible with additional work."
msgstr "编码器-解码器模型的完整图支持：当前强制使用分段模式，但通过额外工作可能实现完整图支持。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:120
msgid ""
"Better integration with Xlite graph mode: the current interaction between"
" ACL graph and Xlite graph is ad-hoc and could be more systematic."
msgstr "与 Xlite 计算图模式的更好集成：当前 ACL 计算图和 Xlite 计算图之间的交互是临时性的，可以更加系统化。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:121
msgid ""
"More efficient pool management: sharing pools across batch descriptors "
"could reduce memory usage."
msgstr "更高效的池管理：跨批次描述符共享池可以减少内存使用。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:90
msgid "This mechanism is implemented in attention backends such as:"
msgstr "此机制在注意力后端中实现，例如："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:92
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/attention_v1.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/attention_v1.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:93
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/mla_v1.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/mla_v1.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:94
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/attention_cp.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/attention_cp.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:95
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/mla_cp.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/mla_cp.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:97
msgid ""
"The important design point is that Ascend full graph support depends on "
"backend-provided `update_graph_params()` hooks. Without that hook, "
"capture alone is not enough to replay the correct attention state."
msgstr ""
"重要的设计点是，Ascend 完整图支持依赖于后端提供的 `update_graph_params()` "
"钩子。没有这个钩子，仅靠捕获不足以重放正确的注意力状态。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:99
msgid "Replay ordering and synchronization"
msgstr "重放顺序与同步"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:101
msgid ""
"`ACLGraphWrapper` synchronizes the current stream before replay in the "
"common path to ensure that host-side parameter updates stay aligned with "
"the graph execution that will consume them. This is especially relevant "
"in asynchronous scheduling or multi-threaded execution."
msgstr ""
"`ACLGraphWrapper` "
"在通用路径的重放前同步当前流，以确保主机侧参数更新与将要使用它们的图执行保持对齐。这在异步调度或多线程执行中尤为重要。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:103
msgid ""
"If ordering is not preserved, the parameter update for iteration *i* can "
"be observed by the replay of iteration *i-1*, or the replay of iteration "
"*i* can start before its own parameter update has completed. In practice,"
" this means the attention operator may run with mismatched runtime "
"metadata, which can cause incorrect results, precision issues, or even "
"hangs. The code keeps a narrower path for the main full-graph eagle case,"
" but the general design assumption is the same: replay must not overtake "
"pending parameter update work."
msgstr ""
"如果顺序未得到保持，迭代 *i* 的参数更新可能被迭代 *i-1* 的重放观察到，或者迭代 *i* "
"的重放可能在它自身的参数更新完成之前就开始。实际上，这意味着注意力算子可能在运行时元数据不匹配的情况下运行，这可能导致错误结果、精度问题甚至挂起。代码为主流的完整图"
" eagle 情况保留了一条更窄的路径，但通用的设计假设是相同的：重放不得超越待处理的参数更新工作。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:105
msgid "Full vs Piecewise on Ascend"
msgstr "Ascend 上的完整图与分段图"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:107
msgid ""
"Upstream docs already define full graph and piecewise graph semantically."
" On Ascend, the practical difference is driven by backend support and "
"resource cost."
msgstr "上游文档已经在语义上定义了完整图和分段图。在 Ascend 上，实际差异由后端支持和资源成本驱动。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:109
msgid "Piecewise mode"
msgstr "分段模式"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:111
msgid ""
"Piecewise mode is the conservative path. It relies on the generic vLLM "
"split execution strategy, then applies ACL graph capture to the non-"
"attention segments selected by the compilation path. On Ascend, this mode"
" is currently the more widely supported option, but it is also the most "
"sensitive to stream pressure because the number of captured graphs scales"
" with model depth."
msgstr ""
"分段模式是保守路径。它依赖通用的 vLLM 拆分执行策略，然后将 ACL 图捕获应用于编译路径选择的非注意力片段。在 Ascend "
"上，此模式是目前更广泛支持的选项，但它也对流压力最敏感，因为捕获的图数量随模型深度而增加。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:113
msgid "Full graph mode"
msgstr "完整图模式"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:115
msgid ""
"Full graph mode is the more performance-oriented path when the attention "
"backend can support runtime parameter patching through "
"`update_graph_params()`. On Ascend, full graph support is tied to those "
"attention-specific update hooks, workspace caching, and replay ordering "
"guarantees."
msgstr ""
"完整图模式是更注重性能的路径，前提是注意力后端能够通过 `update_graph_params()` 支持运行时参数修补。在 Ascend "
"上，完整图支持与那些注意力特定的更新钩子、工作空间缓存和重放顺序保证紧密相关。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:117
msgid "Diagnostics and Operational Notes"
msgstr "诊断与操作说明"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:119
msgid ""
"The simplest way to confirm that graph mode is active is to enable "
"cudagraph metrics and keep log stats enabled. In CLI usage, use "
"`--cudagraph-metrics` and do not pass `--disable-log-stats`. In Python "
"usage, set `cudagraph_metrics=True` and `disable_log_stats=False`. Then "
"inspect the emitted metrics and logs."
msgstr ""
"确认图模式是否激活的最简单方法是启用 cudagraph 指标并保持日志统计开启。在 CLI 使用中，使用 `--cudagraph-"
"metrics` 且不传递 `--disable-log-stats`。在 Python 使用中，设置 "
"`cudagraph_metrics=True` 和 `disable_log_stats=False`。然后检查输出的指标和日志。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:120
msgid ""
"Profiling can also confirm whether replay is happening, and developers "
"can add temporary prints before replay when debugging locally, but those "
"are secondary methods and are not expanded here."
msgstr "性能分析也可以确认重放是否发生，开发者可以在本地调试时在重放前添加临时打印，但这些都是次要方法，此处不展开说明。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:121
msgid ""
"`update_aclgraph_sizes()` is the main implementation point for stream-"
"budget-driven capture-size trimming."
msgstr "`update_aclgraph_sizes()` 是基于流预算驱动的捕获大小调整的主要实现点。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:122
msgid ""
"In debug mode, `ACLGraphWrapper` asserts that replay uses the same tensor"
" addresses recorded during capture."
msgstr "在调试模式下，`ACLGraphWrapper` 断言重放使用与捕获期间记录的相同的张量地址。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:123
msgid ""
"`ASCEND_LAUNCH_BLOCKING=1` is incompatible with ACL graph enablement in "
"the current implementation."
msgstr "在当前实现中，`ASCEND_LAUNCH_BLOCKING=1` 与 ACL 图启用不兼容。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:124
msgid ""
"For debugging inside graph execution, the repo also provides graph-aware "
"print helpers in `vllm_ascend.utils`, but those are developer diagnostics"
" rather than part of the execution design."
msgstr ""
"对于图执行内部的调试，代码库还在 `vllm_ascend.utils` "
"中提供了图感知的打印辅助工具，但这些是开发者诊断工具，而非执行设计的一部分。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:126
msgid "Related Files"
msgstr "相关文件"

